#eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Operation Dudula leader Nhlanhla 'Lux' Dlamini has been granted bail. Dlamini appeared in court after spending the weekend in jail. He is expected back in court on 27 May 2022.    Dlamini has been at the forefront of protests against undocumented foreign nationals. Operation Dudula supporters said Dlamini’s arrest is politically motivated.